[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/comments/86837209","html_url":"https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/issues/2981#issuecomment-86837209","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/2981","id":86837209,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDg2ODM3MjA5","user":{"login":"RobRendell","id":1848870,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE4NDg4NzA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1848870?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell","html_url":"https://github.com/RobRendell","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2015-03-27T06:05:23Z","updated_at":"2015-03-27T06:05:23Z","body":"I created a minimal libgdx project that demonstrates the problem.  Tar-gzip in my dropbox:\n\nhttps://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/16299287/fontSizeIssue.tgz\n\nIt creates two fonts from the one generator, with different sizes and `parameter.incremental = true`.  It also sets `parameter.characters = \"aeiou\"` for both fonts, which means it pregenerates the vowels and then loads the remaining characters incrementally.  You can see that the consonants of both strings are the same size, and the text for what is supposed to be the small font has mixed sizes for the vowels and consonants.\n\n![fontsize](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1848870/6863295/deb22de8-d4a2-11e4-87db-d82a7169f706.png)\n\n```\npublic class FontSizeIssue extends ApplicationAdapter {\n\n    private SpriteBatch batch;\n\n    private FreeTypeFontGenerator generator;\n    private BitmapFont font1;\n    private BitmapFont font2;\n\n    @Override\n    public void create () {\n        batch = new SpriteBatch();\n        generator = new FreeTypeFontGenerator(Gdx.files.internal(\"tubular.ttf\"));\n        FreeTypeFontGenerator.FreeTypeFontParameter parameter1 = new FreeTypeFontGenerator.FreeTypeFontParameter();\n        parameter1.size = 20;\n        parameter1.incremental = true;\n        parameter1.characters = \"aeiou\";\n        font1 = generator.generateFont(parameter1);\n        FreeTypeFontGenerator.FreeTypeFontParameter parameter2 = new FreeTypeFontGenerator.FreeTypeFontParameter();\n        parameter2.size = 40;\n        parameter2.incremental = true;\n        parameter2.characters = \"aeiou\";\n        font2 = generator.generateFont(parameter2);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void render () {\n        Gdx.gl.glClearColor(1, 0, 0, 1);\n        Gdx.gl.glClear(GL20.GL_COLOR_BUFFER_BIT);\n        batch.begin();\n        font1.draw(batch, \"small text\", 100, 100);\n        font2.draw(batch, \"large text\", 100, 200);\n        batch.end();\n    }\n}\n```\n","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/comments/86837209/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"RobRendell","id":1848870,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE4NDg4NzA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1848870?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell","html_url":"https://github.com/RobRendell","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobRendell/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.gi